            <author><name>Hannah Ritchie</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[Globally, aviation accounts for around 2.5% of CO2 emissions. But for many, it accounts for a much larger share. Where in the world do people have the highest emissions from flying?<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/carbon-footprint-flying" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2020/10/per-capita-co2-aviation-adjusted-768x542.png"/></a>]]></summary>
