            <title><![CDATA[Less than half of young Americans voted in the last presidential election]]></title>
            <id>https://ourworldindata.org/usa-electoral-turnout</id>
            <link rel="alternate" href="https://ourworldindata.org/usa-electoral-turnout"/>
            <published>2020-11-02T08:40:53.000Z</published>
            <updated>2020-11-02T13:34:25.000Z</updated>
            <author><name>Bobbie Macdonald</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[40% of eligible voters in the US did not vote in the 2016 election. Young Americans in particular often do not exercise their right to vote – less than half of eligible under-30s voted in the last election.<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/usa-electoral-turnout" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2020/11/voter-turnout-rate-by-age-1-768x542.png"/></a>]]></summary>
            </entry>
